651
00:25:20,267 --> 00:25:21,667
Oh, thanks, Jeanie.

652
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:22,700
'You sure it's this room?'

653
00:25:22,733 --> 00:25:25,833
No, but I was
in here earlier.

654
00:25:25,867 --> 00:25:27,800
Anyway, I was saying,
it's a randomized

