with nursing staff?

680
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:18,700
No.

681
00:26:18,733 --> 00:26:20,533
When did you
realize your mistake?

682
00:26:20,567 --> 00:26:23,467
The patient went into
respiratory arrest at 1534

683
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:27,133
14 minutes into
the magnesium injection.

684
00:26:27,167 --> 00:26:29,233
Continue, Dr. Corday.

685
00:26:29,267 --> 00:26:31,367
Endotracheal
intubation was performed.

686
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,133
Heart rate dropped to 30.

687
00:26:33,167 --> 00:26:35,700
The patient received
IV calcium and atropine.

688
00:26:35,733 --> 00:26:39,767
A transvenous pacing wire was
placed, captured at 1556 hrs.

689
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,667
Who was your
supervising resident?

690
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:44,167
‐ Dr. Benton.
