we should embrace our mistakes

702
00:27:15,667 --> 00:27:19,167
and learn from them
to improve the system.

703
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:20,400
I believe I made this mistake

704
00:27:20,433 --> 00:27:22,433
not because I was
untrained or incompetent

705
00:27:22,467 --> 00:27:27,567
but because I was exhausted,
having been up for 36 hours.

706
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:30,867
If we really want
to‐to cut down on our errors

707
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:34,533
